        <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="LukeGospelPreface">
          <label>Preface to the Gospel of Luke</label>
           <div type="textpart" subtype="subtextunit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="SupplicationPrefaceLuke">
              <label>Supplication in the Preface to the Gospel of Luke</label>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩፡ አምላክ። ዘመሓረነ፡ በረድኤቱ፡
               እምድኅረ፡ ስሕተት፡ ወዑረት። ወኣርኣየነ፡ ተመርሖ፡ እምድኅረ፡ እከይ፡ ወተኃጕሎት፡</ab></div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>ወስብሓት፡ ሎቱ፡ ዕዘዝ፡ አልቦ፡ አምላክ፡ ዘእንበሌሁ።</ab></div>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="title expanded" xml:id="TitlePrefaceLuke"><ab>ንቀድም፡ በረድኤተ፡
             እግዚአብሔር፡ በጽሒፈ፡ መቅድመ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ኅሩይ፡ ፩፡ እም፸ወ፪፡ አርድእት፡ ኅሩያን።</ab></div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="subtextunit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="BiographyLuke">
              <label>Biography of Luke</label>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>ዝንቱሰ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ነበረ፡ ዓቃቤ፡ ሥራይ፡ በኣንጾኪያ። ወኮነ፡ ረድኦ፡
               ለእግዚእነ። ወውእቱ፡ ቀለዮጳ፡ ዘተርእዮ፡ እግዚእነ፡ በፍኖተ፡ ኢማሑስ፡ በዕለተ፡ ትንሣኤ።</ab></div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>ወኣዕረፈ፡ ከዊኖ፡ ሰማዕተ፡ በሮሜ፡ አመ፡ ፳ወ፪፡ ለጥቅምት።</ab></div>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="subtextunit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="EusebianSectionsLuke">
              <label>Statement about the Eusebian Sections in the Gospel of Luke</label>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>ወኍልቈ፡ ኣርእስቲሁ፡ ንኡሳን፡ ፫፻፡ ፵ወ፪።</ab></div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>ወምዕራፋቲሁ፡ በልሳነ፡ ሮሜ፡ ፹፫።</ab></div>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="subtextunit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="TituliLuke">
              <label>Tituli of the Gospel of Luke</label>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>፩፡ ጻሐፍት። ፪፡ ኖሎት። ፫፡ ስምዖን፡ ካህን።</ab></div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>
              <l n="70">፹፩፡ ዘከመ፡ ነስሓ፡ ፈያታዊ።</l>
              <l n="71">፹፪፡ በእንተ፡ ስእለተ፡ ሥጋሁ።</l>
              <l n="72">፹፫፡ ቀለዮጳ፡ ወካልኡ።</l></ab></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2713Luke">
          <label>Bǝsrāta Luqās</label>
             <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="LukeGospelHeadline">
              <label>Headline of the Gospel of Luke</label>
              <ab><seg type="title inscriptio expanded">ብስራተ፡ አብ፡ ትሩፍ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ አሓዱ፡
               እምሰብዓ፡ ወክልኤቱ፡ ኣርድእት።</seg> ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብሩ። <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="Abr"/>
               ወፍቁሩ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="Abr"/> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</ab>
             </div>
             <div type="textpart" subtype="coretext" xml:id="LukeGospel">
               <label>Gospel of Luke</label>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>እስመ፡ ብዙኃን፡ እለ፡ ፈቀዱ፡ ሠሪዓ፡ ዜና፡ ግብር፡ ዘንሕነ፡ ጠየቅናሁ፡ ዘከመ፡
                አይድዑነ፡ እልክቱ፡ እለ፡ ቀደሙ፡ ርእየቶ፡ ወተልእክዎ፡ ለቃል፡ ሊተኒ፡ ረትዓኒ፡ ካዕበ፡ ከመ፡ እጽሓፍ፡ ለከ፡</ab></div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>ወነበሩ፡ በቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡ እንዘ፡ ይሴብሕዎ፡ ወይባርክዎ፡
                ለእግዚአብሔር፡ በኵሉ፡ ጊዜ። አሜን።</ab></div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="ch1">
                  <label>Chapter 1</label>
               </div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="ch2">
                  <label>Chapter 2</label>
