            </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="colophon" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="PostscriptLuke">
              <label>Colophon of the Gospel of Luke</label>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>መልአ፡ ጽሕፈተ፡ <seg type="title subscriptio">ብስራቱ፡ ሉቃስ፡</seg></ab></div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>በዓመተ፡ ፲ወ፬፡ እመንግሥተ፡ አቅላንድዮስ፡ ቄሳር። ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡
               ለቅዱስ፡ ሉቃስ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብሩ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="Abr"/> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ወአሜን።</ab></div>
            </div>
         </div>
       </div>
    </body>
   </text></TEI>